text.tspan: Initial block: set common interfaces in config_db
intr_if: This is created as pins_if with NUM_MAX_INTERRUPTS(set to 64)
IP is expected to have much fewer interrupts
handhake_i: retrieved by dma_env using dma_if
lsio_trigger_i is connected to this signal
- Most components extended from cip_base with the right type parameter
- Ideally, all tests use the same base test class; only the test sequence is changed
Blue Rectange with folder corner: code blocks (initial, tasks, etc)
Dotted blocks: Indicate handles inside parent entity
Alternate dash and dot blocks: component exist sonly in extended IP tb
Light dotted lines: Indicdate handle to instance passed on to components

tspan.tspan: Lightditted lines: Indicate handle to instance passedoin top components

text.tspan: run_phase(): calls run_seq() which creates and runs sequence
All vseqs are eventually derived from cip_base_vseq
- Proivides most commonly used tasks among all vseqs.
- All DMA vseqs are derived from dma_base_vseq
- For each interface a mem_model is instantiated
